charge, let's say,

00:01:18.590 --> 00:01:21.800
z times the electron
charge and it's colliding,

00:01:21.800 --> 00:01:26.810
kind of, with an electron
somewhere else separated

00:01:26.810 --> 00:01:29.840
by some impact parameter b.

00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:31.730
And let's say this
hollow cylinder

00:01:31.730 --> 00:01:35.780
head a shell of thickness db.

00:01:35.780 --> 00:01:37.820
And we started off
with this situation

00:01:37.820 --> 00:01:39.680
where we wanted to say--

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:44.570
